*.pem
# B-033: the parser-bundle DEV signing keypair is committed ON PURPOSE (it is NOT a secret —
# real key management via KMS is tracked in techdebt TD-014). The embedded public key the app
# verifies against is committed too. Production keys are env-injected and never committed.
!backend/keys/dev/spec-signing-private.pem
!backend/keys/dev/spec-signing-public.pem
!android/parsers/src/main/resources/keys/spec-signing-public.pem
